title: Households; key figures
maintainer_displayname: ZBO | Centraal Bureau voor de Statistiek
name: households-key-figures
notes:
This table contains information about the progress of the households in the Netherlands by size and composition and persons by household position, on 1 January.

Data available from: 1995

Status of the figures:
The figures in this table are final.
The production method for data on households has been changed in 2014. As a result data concerning the population on 1 January 2014 may vary between tables. The differences are minimal and only occur in data for 1 January 2014.

From 2014 onwards, institutional households are surveyed on the basis of data from zorgkaartnederland.nl and individuals who receive residential care under the Exceptional Medical Expenses Act (AWBZ). This new method gives better coverage of institutional households. Also from 2014 onwards, institutional households include asylum seekers living in refugee centres and registered in the municipal population register. These two factors have resulted in a shift between institutional and private households. See section 4.

Changes as of 13 February 2015:
None, this is a new table. 
This table replaces a similar table with figures up to 2013, with another classification by type of institution for the people living in institutional households (see section 3).

When will new figures be published?
The final figures of persons in insitutional households by type of institution of the years 1995 untill 2013 will be added during 2015. 
The final figures of 1 January 2015 will be added in the 4th quarter of 2015.
